## 📊 **MANDATORY QUALITY GATES**

### **TECHNICAL QUALITY GATES**

| Gate | Required Evidence |
|------|-------------------|
| Requirements | REQ IDs + measurable acceptance criteria |
| Design | Data flow, RBAC impact, error modes |
| Security | Threat model note or reference |
| Implementation | File change list + rationale |
| Test | Unit + negative + RBAC + edge coverage plan |
| Audit | Event list + sample payload structure |
| Release | Rollback plan + quality summary + grep proof (no banned terms) |

### **PROHIBITED RUNTIME TERMS**
`placeholder`, `mock`, `mocked`, `simulate`, `simulated`, `dummy`, `sample data`, `example data`, `skeleton`, `temp impl`, `stub export`

