## 🔒 **SECURITY & COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS**

### **SECURITY STANDARDS**
- **Authentication**: JWT-based authentication mandatory
- **Authorization**: Role-based access control (RBAC) required
- **Data Protection**: Encryption at rest and in transit
- **Audit Logging**: Comprehensive audit trails
- **Compliance**: SOC 2 Type II compliance target

### **PII & RBAC GOVERNANCE**
- **Financial Data**: Revenue, staff_costs, profit_margin always permission-gated
- **Restricted Access**: Masked data, no error exposure
- **Audit Events**: All sensitive actions logged
- **Data Classification**: Proper data categorization
- **Access Controls**: Granular permission management

### **SECURITY HYGIENE CHECKLIST**
- [ ] No secrets in code
- [ ] No unsafe eval usage
- [ ] Proper CORS configuration
- [ ] Auth guards implemented
- [ ] Input validation complete
- [ ] SQL injection prevention
- [ ] XSS protection enabled
- [ ] CSRF protection active

